Regarding

291
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:47,200
the student rep
for the rally,

292
00:18:48,039 --> 00:18:49,720
I think we should go with Jiang Yan.

293
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,359
Sure, a good choice.

294
00:18:51,359 --> 00:18:51,839
No problem.

295
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,079
Jiang Fan,

296
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,920
you hang out with Lu Xixiao a lot.

297
00:18:59,519 --> 00:19:00,400
Any news from him
lately?

298
00:19:01,559 --> 00:19:02,039
Nah.

299
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,480
We aren't that close.

300
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:04,640
Say that again.

301
00:19:06,119 --> 00:19:06,599
Mostly,
I do the talking.

302
00:19:07,519 --> 00:19:08,319
He's sort of a

303
00:19:08,559 --> 00:19:09,119
listener.

304
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,200
I bet that's true.

305
00:19:11,039 --> 00:19:12,359
Is there a problem?

306
00:19:12,599 --> 00:19:13,599
The office told me

307
00:19:13,759 --> 00:19:15,119
Lu Xixiao signed up for the exam.

308
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:16,039
- Yeah.
- But a few days back,

309
00:19:16,039 --> 00:19:17,319
he was asking around about

310
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:18,279
how to get the

311
00:19:18,279 --> 00:19:19,759
paperwork for studying abroad,

312
00:19:19,759 --> 00:19:20,240
and stuff.

313
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:22,000
But I'm pretty sure his family

314
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,519
never mentioned sending him abroad.

315
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:24,759
Don't you think
we should check

316
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:26,960
with his folks?

317
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,400
If he meant it,

318
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:29,440
we definitely need to.

319
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,640
Lu Xixiao's going abroad?

320
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:32,680
Jiang Fan,

321
00:19:33,599 --> 00:19:34,559
any idea about it?

322
00:19:35,759 --> 00:19:36,799
Aboard? Nor ideal.

323
00:19:37,079 --> 00:19:37,880
Don't get me started.

324
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,279
No, never heard of it.

325
00:19:39,279 --> 00:19:39,640
Never.

326
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:40,960
Kids these days,

327
00:19:41,359 --> 00:19:42,720
