354
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,000
Alright, then.

355
00:20:32,119 --> 00:20:33,119
Mr. Zhao, keep going.

356
00:20:33,599 --> 00:20:34,559
- Sure thing.
- Thanks.

357
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:35,680
Take care, Dean.

358
00:20:36,319 --> 00:20:36,960
That's all.

359
00:20:38,680 --> 00:20:39,240
You hear that?

360
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:41,799
If only you would

361
00:20:42,559 --> 00:20:43,799
