362
00:20:44,799 --> 00:20:46,200
She is seriously making a plan now,

363
00:20:46,799 --> 00:20:49,039
whereas you, at the final stretch of high school...

364
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:50,839
Are you listening?

365
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:53,119
Didn't you tell me to look at her?

366
00:20:54,279 --> 00:20:55,720
I told you to "look up to" her,

367
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,400
