368
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:58,480
What's next? "Looking at" TV?

369
00:20:59,599 --> 00:21:01,279
Find something to learn from her!

370
00:21:02,559 --> 00:21:03,039
Get a move on.

371
00:21:03,559 --> 00:21:04,119
Thanks, Sir.
I'm off.

372
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:18,519
Xixiao, your laundry's done.

373
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:19,759
Is it okay

374
00:21:19,759 --> 00:21:21,000
