375
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,359
Okay, come on in.

376
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:28,440
No problem.

377
00:21:36,759 --> 00:21:38,000
"So Hot."

378
00:21:38,799 --> 00:21:39,319
What?

379
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,640
Your T-shirt.

380
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,680
It says "So Hot" on it.

381
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,640
That doesn't

382
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,000
look like your style.

383
00:21:45,599 --> 00:21:46,960
Is it something special?

384
00:21:50,839 --> 00:21:52,480
I guess it is, at least to me.

385
00:21:54,279 --> 00:21:55,200
I'll put that away for you.

386
00:22:05,039 --> 00:22:05,799
Ms. Chen.

387
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,240
Could you toss that out for me?

388
00:22:11,039 --> 00:22:11,559
Sure.

389
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:24,319
I've handled the paperwork and

390
00:22:24,319 --> 00:22:25,000
