behind your dad's back.

391
00:22:25,839 --> 00:22:26,720
You're all set.

392
00:22:27,359 --> 00:22:27,880
Keep in mind,

393
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:29,160
you owe me a big one.

394
00:22:48,279 --> 00:22:49,319
The meds. Here you are.

395
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,359
Please double-check.

396
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:51,839
Thanks.
No problem.

397
00:22:53,079 --> 00:22:53,880
Next, please.

398
00:22:54,799 --> 00:22:55,680
Just a moment, please.

399
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:28,920
