405
00:23:43,839 --> 00:23:44,599
I'm fine and dandy.

406
00:23:44,599 --> 00:23:45,880
There's nothing wrong with me.

407
00:23:46,039 --> 00:23:46,680
Can you please

408
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:48,359
stop stressing about me when you need to

409
00:23:48,359 --> 00:23:49,200
