410
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:50,559
I just want you to be okay.

411
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,319
I want you back in good health.

412
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:54,160
I can't stand

413
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,319
