438
00:25:54,359 --> 00:25:56,359
Well, your grandma's a sensible woman.

439
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,640
It's just you who never got it.

440
00:26:07,519 --> 00:26:08,759
You took all the money

441
00:26:08,759 --> 00:26:09,559
Dad left behind.

442
00:26:10,039 --> 00:26:10,759
For the last ten years,
there was never

443
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:12,680
