514
00:30:22,079 --> 00:30:23,440
Zhou Wan!

515
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,640
Zhou Wan!

516
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,519
Respected teachers and fellow students,

517
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:45,440
