533
00:31:25,599 --> 00:31:26,599
Someday,

534
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,720
our paths will cross again.

535
00:31:37,599 --> 00:31:38,559
Until then,

536
00:31:39,119 --> 00:31:40,960
