542
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:53,400
Bravo!

543
00:31:54,599 --> 00:31:55,240
To conclude with,

544
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:57,039
let's wish each other

545
00:31:58,599 --> 00:31:59,680
