546
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,559
The world is our oyster!

547
00:32:01,759 --> 00:32:04,039
Bravo!

548
00:32:04,759 --> 00:32:05,720
I wish you all

549
00:32:06,079 --> 00:32:07,359
