550
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,640
The world is your oyster!

551
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:10,079
Thank you!

552
00:32:10,079 --> 00:32:11,160
A brilliant future,

553
00:32:11,559 --> 00:32:12,960
and the world is yours!

