563
00:32:29,319 --> 00:32:30,920
The world is our oyster!

564
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,640
What are you two up to here?

565
00:33:01,519 --> 00:33:02,240
Did you get into a fight?
Yeah.

566
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,440
I started it.

567
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:10,160
Watch your mouth from now on,

568
00:33:11,119 --> 00:33:12,279
or there will be a next time.

569
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:14,519
Am I clear?

570
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:34,920
Seriously, what's going on?

571
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:40,519
I was trying to have your back.

572
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:44,480
So you went after Lu Xixiao first.

573
00:33:47,519 --> 00:33:48,359
Does it matter?

574
00:33:50,680 --> 00:33:51,599
Everyone in school knows

575
00:33:51,599 --> 00:33:52,839
