576
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:54,279
And you still
went to the dean for him.

577
00:33:55,279 --> 00:33:56,079
Don't do that again.

578
00:34:00,039 --> 00:34:01,119
I'm no saint either,

579
00:34:01,759 --> 00:34:02,759
and I don't need your protection.

580
00:34:05,559 --> 00:34:06,920
If we're actually friends,

581
00:34:07,799 --> 00:34:08,679
then stop interfering
with my life and my choices.

582
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:22,639
Finally done with school.

583
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,639
No more homework to deal with.

584
00:34:28,719 --> 00:34:29,719
Wan,

585
00:34:30,039 --> 00:34:30,840
you have to promise

586
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,320
never to forget me.

587
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,159
Got it?

588
00:34:33,159 --> 00:34:34,840
And you better text me back.

589
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:35,519
You

590
00:34:35,519 --> 00:34:36,840
always leave me on read.

591
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,679
I didn't mean to.

592
00:34:39,239 --> 00:34:40,079
If you pull that again,
I'll show up

593
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,800
and camp out on your doorstep.

594
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:43,519
Welcome.
For real?

595
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:45,360
I'll be glued to you for good, then.

596
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:46,880
You're on.

597
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:51,760
Wan,

598
00:34:52,159 --> 00:34:53,039
this is the last time
we walk home together.

599
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:55,400
I'm gonna miss you.

600
00:34:56,079 --> 00:34:57,239
Make sure you hit the books

601
00:34:57,239 --> 00:34:58,239
while you're home.

602
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:58,880
Got it?

603
00:35:00,920 --> 00:35:01,679
Don't worry about me.

604
00:35:02,719 --> 00:35:04,639
Seriously, put the phone away,

605
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:06,199
and focus on studying this week.

606
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,280
I know.
If you're struggling,

607
00:35:08,199 --> 00:35:08,840
just come over.

608
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,239
Saves you from text-bombing me.

609
00:35:11,159 --> 00:35:12,880
I knew you had a soft spot for me!

610
00:35:15,159 --> 00:35:15,880
I'm heading out.

611
00:35:18,079 --> 00:35:18,480
Bye.
Bye.

612
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,480
Dad.

613
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,119
You're home.

614
00:35:57,559 --> 00:35:58,599
You're already set for university,

615
00:35:59,000 --> 00:36:00,360
why do you still go to school every day?

616
00:36:04,159 --> 00:36:05,280
You don't want to be home?

617
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:09,599
No.

618
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,159
We had a pep rally today,

619
00:36:12,159 --> 00:36:13,159
and as student rep,

620
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,079
I had to give a speech.

621
00:36:17,639 --> 00:36:18,719
I just want to remind you,

622
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,519
just because you're set,

623
00:36:20,639 --> 00:36:21,559
doesn't mean you can slack off.

624
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:24,559
You need to aim for the fast track,

625
00:36:24,559 --> 00:36:25,719
and get that top-tier degree.

626
00:36:26,199 --> 00:36:27,000
Don't you dare

627
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:28,079
let me down.

628
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,039
You hear me?

629
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,159
Noted.

630
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:42,039
Look at you, a student rep

631
00:36:42,639 --> 00:36:44,000
and you didn't even bother to dress up.

632
00:36:44,519 --> 00:36:46,119
You look like a total mess.

633
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:48,639
Don't screw up again.

634
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:04,159
Anything else?

635
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:11,039
If not, get to bed.

636
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:12,199
Don't stay up late.

637
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:52,039
But I think I know better than her

638
00:37:52,199 --> 00:37:53,119
what you are.

639
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,519
Are you gonna hit your brother?

640
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,039
Try saying that again,

641
00:37:57,159 --> 00:37:58,639
I'll punch your lights out.

642
00:37:59,159 --> 00:38:00,400
I was trying to have your back.

643
00:38:00,480 --> 00:38:01,880
If we're actually friends,

644
00:38:02,719 --> 00:38:03,559
then stop interfering
with my life and my choices.

645
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:20,920
Ping.

646
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:25,119
I graduated!

647
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:28,039
Seriously? That's awesome!

648
00:38:30,679 --> 00:38:31,920
Congrats.

649
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,239
Thanks, Ping.

650
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:35,199
Good thing you didn't turn out like me:

651
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:36,400
slacking off in school,

652
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:38,000
and ending up a grease monkey.

653
00:38:39,679 --> 00:38:40,960
Can't you find something nice to say?

654
00:38:41,199 --> 00:38:42,000
I'm going back to work.

655
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:49,559
Xixiao.

656
00:38:51,119 --> 00:38:52,199
Try not to miss me too badly.

657
00:38:54,519 --> 00:38:55,239
As if.

658
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:56,800
Why would I miss you?

659
00:38:57,719 --> 00:38:58,639
We're gonna be half a world apart,

660
00:38:58,639 --> 00:39:00,079
who else are you gonna miss?

661
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,599
Besides, I bandaged this for you.

662
00:39:04,559 --> 00:39:05,880
Once I'm not around,

663
00:39:06,239 --> 00:39:06,840
who's gonna

664
00:39:06,840 --> 00:39:07,960
wrap you up in pretty gauze?

665
00:39:08,719 --> 00:39:09,679
So you're hoping that I

666
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,519
get hurt every day?

667
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,440
Thought you said you aren’t coming today.

668
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:14,400
Now what? A fight?

669
00:39:15,519 --> 00:39:16,440
I missed you.

670
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:17,599
Alright?

671
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:18,719
Can't I come by and see you?

672
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,519
Sure, knock yourself out.

673
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:23,320
Wait, were you actually here to see...

674
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,960
Shut up. Just shut up.

675
00:39:27,159 --> 00:39:28,000
You gotta admit,

676
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,559
Zhou Wan is a real one.

677
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,440
You guys had a falling out,

678
00:39:31,599 --> 00:39:32,519
but she still

679
00:39:32,519 --> 00:39:33,719
covered for your studying abroad.

680
00:39:35,719 --> 00:39:36,199
What?

681
00:39:36,559 --> 00:39:37,400
No, never mind.

682
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:38,519
Forget it.

683
00:39:47,679 --> 00:39:48,159
Where'd he go?

684
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:50,480
Left his tools all over the place.

685
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:52,840
If he doesn't hit the books,

686
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:54,360
he'll end up a grease monkey too.

687
00:39:55,920 --> 00:39:56,840
You said that on purpose!

688
00:40:34,159 --> 00:40:34,800
Lu Xixiao!

689
00:40:35,199 --> 00:40:36,719
The school's closed. What are you up to?

690
00:40:36,719 --> 00:40:37,719
I'm running late.

691
00:42:19,679 --> 00:42:21,400
Hello, there!

692
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,800
You smell so good.

693
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,039
Long time no see.

694
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:02,679
It's been a while.
